    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 2.5",
    "body" : "<p>I don't know why you are dividing by 100 but here my assumption <code>int a;</code></p>\n\n<pre><code>int b = (int) Math.ceil( ((double)a) / 100);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>or </p>\n\n<pre><code>int b = (int) Math.ceil( a / 100.0);\n</code></pre>\n"
