    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Assuming a as double and we need a rounded number with no decimal place . Use Math.round() function.<br>\nThis goes as my solution . </p>\n\n<pre><code>double a = 0.99999;\nint rounded_a = (int)Math.round(a);\nSystem.out.println(\"a:\"+rounded_a );\n\nOutput : \na:1\n</code></pre>\n"
