    "question_id" : 4540684,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>The easiest way to do this is just: \nYou will receive a float or double and want it to convert it to the closest round up then just do <code>  System.out.println((int)Math.ceil(yourfloat)); </code>\nit'll work perfectly</p>\n"
