    "question_id" : 4540684,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>Just another option. Use basics of math:</p>\n<p><code>Math.ceil(p / K)</code> is same as <code>((p-1) // K) + 1</code></p>\n"
  } ],
